        <li>tale_noun->[pawn_nameShortDef] chased away by enemies</li>
        <li>image->[pawn_nameFull] running frantically [circumstance_group]</li>
        <li>image->[pawn_nameFull] sprinting [circumstance_group]</li>
        <li>image->[pawn_nameFull] tucked behind a [terrainfeature], hiding [circumstance_group]</li>
        <li>image->[pawn_nameFull] putting up a fighting retreat [circumstance_group]</li>
        <li>image->[pawn_nameFull] casually strolling away [circumstance_group]</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase->as [quantity_adjphrase] [enemy]s chase</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase->while [quantity_adjphrase] [enemy]s search</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase->from [quantity_adjphrase] [enemy]s</li>
        <li>circumstance_phrase->from [quantity_adjphrase] enemy [animal]s</li>
